{
  "stem": "9963.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He couldn't pay for me, you know, in a big school like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I couldn't go over there, so I took apprenticeship as a tailor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I went to another city to learn to be a tailor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was there three years, finished the tailoring, the apprenticeship, so the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war broke out, so the-- I already started making money, because the three years was finished.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the war broke out, and the-- right away the Germans said-- we went away, and later we come back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans took us right away to work in the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what is my schooling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had ready-made shoes, what he was making.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had a little stall and making ready-made shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the relationship with the parents was very good because we were very-- with the discipline, we-- the father had the first and last word, you know, in the house.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was very good relationship, very close.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the-- the thing is that I was so little at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because, as I told you before, I spent my whole young years learning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later, when I went away to another city to be in apprenticeship, again, the only time when I came home when I was with my father and mother was only on the holidays, on Pesach, and on the high holidays.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there's very little that I could really have like he-- you know, a father goes out to the beach with their children, and plays ball with the children, and things like this.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even though we were close-- we loved each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But still, I was so occupied with different things, what-- I was very little at home.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
